                    <li>Speakeasy-style bars</li>
                    <li>Intimate dining rooms</li>
                    <li>Architectural significance</li>
                  </ul>
                </div>
                
                <div class="area-card">
                  <h3>üåÜ Bunker Hill</h3>
                  <p>Modern high-rise dining with panoramic city views. Ideal for special occasions and couples who want to see LA from above.</p>
                  <ul>
                    <li>Rooftop dining options</li>
                    <li>City skyline views</li>
                    <li>Modern architecture</li>
                    <li>Elevated dining experiences</li>
                  </ul>
                </div>
              </div>
            </section>

            <section class="downtown-tips">
              <h2>Downtown LA Date Night Tips</h2>
              
