                  <h3>üåÉ Evening Timing</h3>
                  <p>Plan for 7-8 PM reservations to catch the city lights coming on. The skyline becomes magical as the sun sets behind the mountains.</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="tip-card">
                  <h3>üé≠ Pre/Post-Dinner Activities</h3>
                  <p>Extend your evening with nearby entertainment: concerts at the Walt Disney Concert Hall, shows at the Ahmanson Theatre, or drinks at rooftop bars.</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="tip-card">
                  <h3>üëî Dress Code</h3>
                  <p>Downtown LA restaurants range from casual to upscale. Check the restaurant's website or call ahead to ensure appropriate attire for your chosen venue.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </section>

            <section class="downtown-experiences">
              <h2>Unique Downtown LA Date Night Experiences</h2>
              
              <div class="experiences-grid">
                <div class="experience-card">
                  <h3>üåÖ Sunset Rooftop Dining</h3>
                  <p>Book a rooftop restaurant for 6:30-7:00 PM to enjoy dinner with a spectacular sunset over the city skyline. Perfect for romantic conversations and Instagram-worthy moments.</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="experience-card">
                  <h3>üç∏ Speakeasy Bar Hopping</h3>
                  <p>Explore DTLA's hidden speakeasies and craft cocktail bars. Many require reservations or have secret entrances, adding an element of adventure to your date night.</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="experience-card">
                  <h3>üé® Art Walk Dining</h3>
                  <p>Combine dinner with gallery visits during the monthly Downtown Art Walk. Many restaurants offer special menus and extended hours for the event.</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="experience-card">
                  <h3>üéµ Live Music & Dining</h3>
                  <p>Enjoy dinner with live music at venues that combine great food with entertainment. From jazz clubs to acoustic performances, DTLA offers diverse musical dining experiences.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </section>

            <section class="downtown-transportation">
              <h2>Getting Around Downtown LA</h2>
              
              <div class="transportation-options">
                <div class="transport-card">
                  <h3>üöá Metro Rail</h3>
                  <p>The Metro system makes DTLA easily accessible from throughout LA County. Multiple lines converge downtown, making it convenient for date nights without driving.</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="transport-card">
                  <h3>üöó Ride-Sharing</h3>
                  <p>Uber and Lyft are popular options for downtown date nights, especially when planning to enjoy cocktails. Many restaurants offer valet service as well.</p>
                </div>
                
